    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deo sancto Mercurio Honoratus <lb n="2"/>conqueror numini tuo me per<lb break="no" n="3"/>didisse rotas duas et vaccas quat<lb break="no" n="4"/>tuor et resculas plurimas de <lb n="5"/>hospitiolo meo <lb n="6"/>rogaverim genium nu<lb break="no" n="7"/>minis tuui <note>sic</note> ut ei qui mihi fraudem <lb n="8"/>fecerit sanitatem ei non per<lb break="no" n="9"/>mittas nec iacere nec sedere nec <lb n="10"/>bibere nec manducare si baro <lb n="11"/>si mulier si puer si puella si servus <lb n="12"/>si liber nissi <note>sic</note> meam rem ad me <lb n="13"/>pertulerit et meam concordiam <lb n="14"/>habuerit iteratis praecibus <note>sic</note> ro<lb break="no" n="15"/>go numen tuum ut petitio mea <lb n="16"/>statim pareat me vindica<lb break="no" n="17"/>tum esse a maiestate tua
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gebet für Gerechtigkeit.</p>
            </div>
